  "short_description": "Logic meets precision in SPIN Protocol, a colorful and challenging puzzle game about rotating nodes. Each circuit presents a unique challenge, with different node types introducing special behaviors that will put your problem solving skills to the test. Are you ready to spin your way to victory?",
