  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In SPIN Protocol, your goal is clear: redirect signals to activate every Receiver Node with the correct color. But don’t be fooled- the path to victory is rarely straightforward...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Signals of different colors cannot mix or cross, and sometimes the most obvious path is not the correct one:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >          <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342810/extras/7e032ab4305d6e7633e30107e8f04a1c.poster.avif?t=1742346638\" width=520 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342810/extras/7e032ab4305d6e7633e30107e8f04a1c.webm?t=1742346638\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342810/extras/7e032ab4305d6e7633e30107e8f04a1c.mp4?t=1742346638\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you progress, new types of nodes are introduced. Fusion Nodes can mix two colors to create a new one:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >          <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342810/extras/bad3466a4d6abc2316bead812daa4594.poster.avif?t=1742346638\" width=520 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342810/extras/bad3466a4d6abc2316bead812daa4594.webm?t=1742346638\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342810/extras/bad3466a4d6abc2316bead812daa4594.mp4?t=1742346638\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bridge Nodes allow signals to cross paths without interference:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >          <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342810/extras/2d2865637a5a3c01becde490bb43f366.poster.avif?t=1742346638\" width=520 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342810/extras/2d2865637a5a3c01becde490bb43f366.webm?t=1742346638\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342810/extras/2d2865637a5a3c01becde490bb43f366.mp4?t=1742346638\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >and much, much more...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For perfectionists, merely solving a level might not be enough. Earn a perfect score by completing levels within the time and rotation limits:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >           <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342810/extras/ce127ff07d8eb3fd8c20f8afc5a68848.poster.avif?t=1742346638\" width=520 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342810/extras/ce127ff07d8eb3fd8c20f8afc5a68848.webm?t=1742346638\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342810/extras/ce127ff07d8eb3fd8c20f8afc5a68848.mp4?t=1742346638\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With over 60 levels of increasing difficulty, SPIN Protocol offers a satisfying blend of simplicity and depth.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Effortless controls:</strong> Rotate nodes with a single button, fully playable with either a mouse, keyboard or controller.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Over 60 handcrafted levels:</strong> With each new circuit, you'll face new challenges. As you progress and discover new game mechanics, these levels will become more complex and intricate.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Minimalistic  aesthetic:</strong> Immerse yourself in a clean, retro-futuristic visual and audio design</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multi-language support</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Steam Achievements</strong></p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In SPIN Protocol, your goal is clear: redirect signals to activate every Receiver Node with the correct color. But don’t be fooled- the path to victory is rarely straightforward...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Signals of different colors cannot mix or cross, and sometimes the most obvious path is not the correct one:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >          <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342810/extras/7e032ab4305d6e7633e30107e8f04a1c.poster.avif?t=1742346638\" width=520 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342810/extras/7e032ab4305d6e7633e30107e8f04a1c.webm?t=1742346638\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342810/extras/7e032ab4305d6e7633e30107e8f04a1c.mp4?t=1742346638\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you progress, new types of nodes are introduced. Fusion Nodes can mix two colors to create a new one:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >          <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342810/extras/bad3466a4d6abc2316bead812daa4594.poster.avif?t=1742346638\" width=520 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342810/extras/bad3466a4d6abc2316bead812daa4594.webm?t=1742346638\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342810/extras/bad3466a4d6abc2316bead812daa4594.mp4?t=1742346638\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bridge Nodes allow signals to cross paths without interference:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >          <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342810/extras/2d2865637a5a3c01becde490bb43f366.poster.avif?t=1742346638\" width=520 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342810/extras/2d2865637a5a3c01becde490bb43f366.webm?t=1742346638\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342810/extras/2d2865637a5a3c01becde490bb43f366.mp4?t=1742346638\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >and much, much more...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For perfectionists, merely solving a level might not be enough. Earn a perfect score by completing levels within the time and rotation limits:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >           <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342810/extras/ce127ff07d8eb3fd8c20f8afc5a68848.poster.avif?t=1742346638\" width=520 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342810/extras/ce127ff07d8eb3fd8c20f8afc5a68848.webm?t=1742346638\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342810/extras/ce127ff07d8eb3fd8c20f8afc5a68848.mp4?t=1742346638\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With over 60 levels of increasing difficulty, SPIN Protocol offers a satisfying blend of simplicity and depth.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Effortless controls:</strong> Rotate nodes with a single button, fully playable with either a mouse, keyboard or controller.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Over 60 handcrafted levels:</strong> With each new circuit, you'll face new challenges. As you progress and discover new game mechanics, these levels will become more complex and intricate.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Minimalistic  aesthetic:</strong> Immerse yourself in a clean, retro-futuristic visual and audio design</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multi-language support</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Steam Achievements</strong></p></li></ul>",
